snippet.title: Spacefolk City Launch Trailer | Available Now on Oculus
snippet.description:
Available Now on the Oculus Store!
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3566126356743668/

Spacefolk City is a funky, casual take on the city building genre! Construct a floating city in space, decorate it with a variety of absurd items, and keep your Spacefolk citizens happy! Developed by Moon Mode, and published by Beyond Frames.

Join our Discord community: https://discord.com/invite/cTFmqmNep7
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/SpacefolkCity

#OculusQuest #OculusRift #SteamVR
